# lumigo-python-wrapper :stars:

![CircleCI](https://circleci.com/gh/lumigo-io/lumigo-python-wrapper/tree/master.svg?style=svg&circle-token=d98d1b95f34b49be2caa58c49d8a70d6a7587b88)
